        <p>Round-the-clock emergency care with experienced physicians ready to handle critical situations at any hour.</p>
        <a href="tel:9136373182" class="learn-more">Call Now <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></a>
      </div>

      <div class="service-card reveal">
        <div class="service-icon"><i class="fas fa-heartbeat"></i></div>
        <h3>ICU & Critical Care</h3>
        <p>Intensive Care Unit with Ventilator, CPAP &amp; Defibrillator support for critical and life-threatening conditions.</p>
        <a href="#appointment" class="learn-more">Learn More <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></a>
      </div>

      <div class="service-card reveal">
        <div class="service-icon"><i class="fas fa-stethoscope"></i></div>
        <h3>General Medicine</h3>
        <p>Expert outpatient consultations for fevers, infections, chronic conditions and preventive health check-ups.</p>
        <a href="#appointment" class="learn-more">Book Consult <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></a>
      </div>

      <div class="service-card reveal">
        <div class="service-icon"><i class="fas fa-scalpel-path"></i></div>
        <h3>General Surgery</h3>
        <p>Comprehensive surgical procedures performed by experienced surgeons in a fully equipped operation theatre.</p>
        <a href="#appointment" class="learn-more">Learn More <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></a>
      </div>

      <div class="service-card reveal">
        <div class="service-icon"><i class="fas fa-baby"></i></div>
        <h3>Paediatrics</h3>
        <p>Dedicated child healthcare — from newborn care to adolescent health — with gentle, expert paediatricians.</p>
        <a href="#appointment" class="learn-more">Book Consult <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></a>
      </div>

      <div class="service-card reveal">
        <div class="service-icon"><i class="fas fa-flask"></i></div>
        <h3>Pathology Lab</h3>
        <p>In-house pathology for fast, accurate blood tests, urine analysis and all routine investigations on-site.</p>
        <a href="#appointment" class="learn-more">Learn More <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></a>
      </div>

      <div class="service-card reveal">
        <div class="service-icon"><i class="fas fa-walking"></i></div>
        <h3>Physiotherapy</h3>
        <p>Rehabilitative physiotherapy for post-surgical recovery, sports injuries, and musculoskeletal disorders.</p>
        <a href="#appointment" class="learn-more">Book Session <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></a>
      </div>

      <div class="service-card reveal">
        <div class="service-icon"><i class="fas fa-gem"></i></div>
        <h3>Kidney Stone Centre</h3>
        <p>Specialised diagnosis and treatment for kidney stones using the latest non-invasive and surgical techniques.</p>
        <a href="#appointment" class="learn-more">Learn More <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></a>
      </div>

      <div class="service-card reveal">
        <div class="service-icon"><i class="fas fa-brain"></i></div>
        <h3>Neurology &amp; Psychiatry</h3>
        <p>Expert care for neurological disorders, mental health conditions, and psychiatric consultations with empathy.</p>
        <a href="#appointment" class="learn-more">Book Consult <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></a>
      </div>

      <div class="service-card reveal">
        <div class="service-icon"><i class="fas fa-ear-listen"></i></div>
