        <p>Specialised diagnosis and treatment for Ear, Nose and Throat conditions across all age groups.</p>
        <a href="#appointment" class="learn-more">Book Consult <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></a>
      </div>

      <div class="service-card reveal">
        <div class="service-icon"><i class="fas fa-hand-dots"></i></div>
        <h3>Dermatology</h3>
        <p>Comprehensive skin care — treating acne, eczema, psoriasis, infections and cosmetic skin concerns.</p>
        <a href="#appointment" class="learn-more">Book Consult <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></a>
      </div>

      <div class="service-card reveal">
        <div class="service-icon"><i class="fas fa-bone"></i></div>
        <h3>Orthopedics &amp; Joint &amp; Spine</h3>
        <p>Advanced orthopedic surgery, joint replacement, and spine care for fractures, arthritis and back pain.</p>
        <a href="#appointment" class="learn-more">Learn More <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></a>
      </div>

      <div class="service-card reveal">
        <div class="service-icon"><i class="fas fa-syringe"></i></div>
