        <p>Holistic diabetes management including blood sugar monitoring, medication, diet counselling and foot care.</p>
        <a href="#appointment" class="learn-more">Book Consult <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></a>
      </div>

      <div class="service-card reveal">
        <div class="service-icon"><i class="fas fa-weight-scale"></i></div>
        <h3>Liposuction &amp; Weight Management</h3>
        <p>Safe, medically supervised weight management programmes and liposuction procedures by trained specialists.</p>
        <a href="#appointment" class="learn-more">Learn More <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></a>
